        "subtopicId": "4.9",
        "title": "Magnetic field",
        "digitizedText": "### 1) Magnetic field\nRegion where ferrous materials (ferum) experience force ($\\text{N} \\rightarrow \\text{S}$)\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <svg class=\"sme-diagram\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" viewBox=\"0 0 300 150\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<!-- Magnet -->\n<rect x=\"100\" y=\"50\" width=\"100\" height=\"30\" class=\"sme-axis\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" />\n<text class=\"sme-text\" x=\"115\" y=\"70\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\">N</text>\n<text class=\"sme-text\" x=\"175\" y=\"70\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\">S</text>\n<path d=\"M 150 50 L 150 80\" class=\"sme-axis\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"4,4\" fill=\"none\" />\n\n<!-- Field Lines Top -->\n<path d=\"M 120 50 C 120 20, 180 20, 180 50\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" />\n<path d=\"M 110 50 C 110 0, 190 0, 190 50\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" />\n<!-- Arrows top -->\n<polygon points=\"150,28 145,33 145,23\" class=\"sme-marker-primary\" />\n<polygon points=\"150,14 145,19 145,9\" class=\"sme-marker-primary\" />\n\n<!-- Field Lines Bottom -->\n<path d=\"M 120 80 C 120 110, 180 110, 180 80\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" />\n<path d=\"M 110 80 C 110 130, 190 130, 190 80\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" />\n<!-- Arrows bottom -->\n<polygon points=\"150,102 145,97 145,107\" class=\"sme-marker-primary\" />\n<polygon points=\"150,116 145,111 145,121\" class=\"sme-marker-primary\" />\n\n<!-- Compass -->\n<circle cx=\"230\" cy=\"65\" r=\"15\" stroke=\"red\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" />\n<path d=\"M 220 65 L 240 65\" stroke=\"red\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" />\n<polygon points=\"240,65 235,60 235,70\" fill=\"red\" />\n</svg>\n</div>\n\ncompass will follow direction of magnetic field line.\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <svg class=\"sme-diagram\" width=\"400\" height=\"150\" viewBox=\"0 0 400 150\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<!-- Magnet 1 -->\n<rect x=\"50\" y=\"50\" width=\"80\" height=\"30\" class=\"sme-axis\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" />\n<text class=\"sme-text\" x=\"60\" y=\"70\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\">N</text>\n<text class=\"sme-text\" x=\"110\" y=\"70\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\">S</text>\n<path d=\"M 90 50 L 90 80\" class=\"sme-axis\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n\n<!-- Field lines 1 (further) -->\n<path d=\"M 65 50 C 65 10, 115 10, 115 50\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n<path d=\"M 55 50 C 55 -10, 125 -10, 125 50\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n<path d=\"M 65 80 C 65 120, 115 120, 115 80\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n<path d=\"M 55 80 C 55 140, 125 140, 125 80\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n\n<text class=\"sme-text\" x=\"70\" y=\"140\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"red\">further lines</text>\n\n<!-- Magnet 2 -->\n<rect x=\"250\" y=\"50\" width=\"80\" height=\"30\" class=\"sme-axis\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" />\n<text class=\"sme-text\" x=\"260\" y=\"70\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\">N</text>\n<text class=\"sme-text\" x=\"310\" y=\"70\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"14\">S</text>\n<path d=\"M 290 50 L 290 80\" class=\"sme-axis\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n\n<!-- Field lines 2 (closer) -->\n<path d=\"M 265 50 C 265 20, 315 20, 315 50\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n<path d=\"M 260 50 C 260 10, 320 10, 320 50\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n<path d=\"M 255 50 C 255 0, 325 0, 325 50\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n\n<path d=\"M 265 80 C 265 110, 315 110, 315 80\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n<path d=\"M 260 80 C 260 120, 320 120, 320 80\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n<path d=\"M 255 80 C 255 130, 325 130, 325 80\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n\n<text class=\"sme-text\" x=\"240\" y=\"130\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"red\">closer magnetic</text>\n<text class=\"sme-text\" x=\"240\" y=\"145\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"red\">field line means</text>\n<text class=\"sme-text\" x=\"240\" y=\"160\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"red\">stronger magnet</text>\n</svg>\n</div>\n\nHow to demagnetised magnet?\n1) Hammer it repeatedly\n2) Heat it up strongly\n3) Put it in solenoid with AC current and decrease the current gradually to zero.\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <svg class=\"sme-diagram\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 100\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<!-- Solenoid -->\n<path d=\"M 40 40 Q 45 20 50 40 T 60 40 T 70 40 T 80 40 T 90 40 T 100 40 T 110 40 T 120 40\" class=\"sme-line-primary\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" />\n<rect x=\"45\" y=\"30\" width=\"70\" height=\"20\" class=\"sme-axis\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n<text class=\"sme-text\" x=\"50\" y=\"45\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\">N</text>\n<text class=\"sme-text\" x=\"100\" y=\"45\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"12\">S</text>\n<!-- AC source -->\n<path d=\"M 40 40 L 40 80 L 70 80\" class=\"sme-axis\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n<path d=\"M 120 40 L 120 80 L 90 80\" class=\"sme-axis\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n<circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"80\" r=\"10\" class=\"sme-axis\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n<path d=\"M 75 80 Q 77 75 80 80 T 85 80\" class=\"sme-axis\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" />\n</svg>\n</div>",
